{"word":"εἴβω","slug":"εἴβω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἴβω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>epic form of <a href='S:λείβω'><el>λείβω</el></a>,\n<p/><i>to drop, let fall in drops</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to trickle down</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/>"}]}